life-insurance business, as well as strong improvements in non-life
insurance and miscellaneous activities. Operating profit from health and
accident insurance eased to Fl 11m from Fl 12m.
Total turnover rose by 13.2 per cent to Fl 4.43bn. The company said turnover
and earnings in the US were considerably higher, but it gave no details.
