FT  13 MAY 92 / UK Company News: The Battle For Midland
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Midland Bank will appeal on Friday to a hearing of the full council of the
Takeover Panel following yesterday's ruling by the panel's executive that
Midland should provide Lloyds with financial information it has already
given to Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation.
